            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "保利置業上月合同銷售按年跌37.5% 首4個月則升9.15%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">保利置業(00119)公布，今年4月份實現合同銷售35億元(人民幣‧下同)，較去年同期減少37.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"保利置業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00119-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"保利置業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00119-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">保利置業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內合同銷售涉及樓面13.9萬平方米，均價每平方米2.49萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若將今年首4個月累積計算，該公司累計實現合同銷售179億元，按年升9.15%；涉及樓面66.2萬平方米，均價每平方米2.71萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14912147-%e4%bf%9d%e5%88%a9%e7%bd%ae%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c37-5-%e9%a6%964%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e5%89%87%e5%8d%879-15",
